                                    "id": "109802f2",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "Receive Support and Encouragement",
                                        "header_size": "h3",
                                        "_animation": "fadeInUp",
                                        "animation_duration": "slow"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "76f86263",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Find comfort in knowing that you're not alone on your path to healing. Our blog provides a supportive space where you can connect with others who have walked similar paths, share your own experiences, and receive words of encouragement and understanding from our community of readers.</p>",
