                                    "id": "b9224cc",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "title": "Explore Practical Resources",
                                        "header_size": "h3",
                                        "_animation": "fadeInUp",
                                        "animation_duration": "slow"
                                    },
                                    "widgetType": "heading",
                                    "elType": "widget"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "1d72ca72",
                                    "settings": {
                                        "editor": "<p>Access practical resources, tools, and tips to support you in coping with loss and navigating the grieving process. From self-care practices and mindfulness techniques to support groups and therapy resources, our blog offers valuable guidance to help you find your way forward with courage and compassion. Explore personal narratives of individuals who have experienced loss\u2014whether it be the loss of a loved one, a job, a relationship, or a sense of identity.</p><p>Gain insight into different perspectives on loss and grief, from coping strategies and healing practices to spiritual beliefs and philosophical reflections. Through their stories, you'll find inspiration in the resilience and strength of the human spirit as they navigate the complexities of grief and emerge stronger on the other side.</p>",
                                        "paragraph_spacing": {
                                            "unit": "px",
                                            "size": 24,
                                            "sizes": []
                                        },
                                        "_animation": "fadeInUp",
                                        "animation_duration": "slow"
                                    },
